<plot>It's the day Ilse-Margret Vogel has been waiting for - the day the Axis powers fall to the Allies and World War II ends. But for Ilse, a resistance fighter and political activist who has risked her life for a decade rescuing Jews and other refugees from Nazi fascism, the end brings only a tribulation more profound than any she's yet endured.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130698</url></doc>
